These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, marigold
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, vegafina, blend
House: colonial, craftsman, wooden
1. the person who growsmarigold is the wooden house##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsamaryllis##2
3. the craftsman house is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |   3   |
| Flower        | marigold | balloon-flower | amaryllis |
| Cigar         | blend    | old-henry     | vegafina  |
| House   | wooden     | craftsman     | colonial  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, february, july
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, roller, van
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, sports
1. the person driving the roller is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |        3        |
| Birthday   | april    | february       | july             |
| Transport      | roller  | van | airplane      |
| Movie-Genre        | comedy | drama    | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, amaryllis, poppy
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, whist
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike, roller
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing chess is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the taxi is between the person who growspoppy and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Flower           | poppy    | aconite   | amaryllis |
| Game   | bridge | chess   | whist         |
| Transport         | motorbike     | taxi | roller     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, german, colombian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, april
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, project-manager, manager
1. the project-manager is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the manager##1
3. the manager is between the person who's birthday is in december and the polish##2
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the german##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Nationality   | colombian    | german  | polish     |
| Birthday   | december       | april   | june       |
| Job     | dressmaker | manager | project-manager |

