.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, rugby, handball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, videographer, dressmaker
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the videographer##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's sport is cycling##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Sport   | handball | rugby   | cycling   |
| Birthday           | september   | february | july     |
| Job     | architect   | dressmaker    | videographer |

