.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, oliveros, havana
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, american, colombian
There are 3 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, coral
1. the colombian is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
3. the person who likes grey is between the american and the person who likes coral##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |
| Cigar         | oliveros   | montecristo | havana |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian      | american  |
| Color   | coral      | grey   | lilac |

