.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, guinea-pig
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, poker
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, juice
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person drinking mirinda and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Pet   | lizard    | guinea-pig    | rat |
| Game         | backgammon   | poker     | scrabble     |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | juice | mirinda     |

