.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
City: berlin, colone, boston
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, russian, colombian
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, bird
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is between the russian and the owner of the chinchilla##2
4. the russian is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| City         | boston | berlin | colone  |
| Nationality   | russian        | colombian        | australian |
| Pet         | frog         | bird    | chinchilla   |

