.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, march, november
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, fanta
House: cape-cod, modern, colonial
1. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the colonial house is between the cape-cod house and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday         | november | march  | september  |
| Beverage         | fanta    | mirinda | coffee |
| House   | cape-cod    | colonial       | modern  |

