.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, videographer, writer
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, domino
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, december, july
1. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the teacher is between the person playing snooker and the writer##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Job   | videographer       | teacher         | writer      |
| Game   | snooker | domino       | whist |
| Birthday         | july     | december | january |

