.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, backgammon-climbing, turquise
3 different games are played: bridge, poker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, october
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person playing bridge is between the person who likes turquise and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Color         | turquise | grey  | backgammon-climbing |
| Game   | poker      | bridge       | backgammon          |
| Birthday         | january  | september | october        |

