.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-12::.
House: farmhouse, craftsman, gothic-revival
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, soccer, ice-hockey
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, water
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3       |
| House           | craftsman   | farmhouse | gothic-revival |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | skiing     | soccer       |
| Beverage   | cola    | mirinda | water       |

