.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, may
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster, game
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, tram, car
1. the game-smoker is between the person driving the car and the person who's birthday is in may##2
2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Birthday          | june      | march | may     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | game  | dunhill     |
| Transport         | car  | airplane | tram |

