2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the owner of the frog is between the person playing snooker and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Flower         | aconite | iris | tulip |
| Pet           | rabbit   | frog   | goldfish |
| Game   | snooker     | monopoly | domino   |

