1. the person playing bridge is between the alhambra-smoker and the person traveling to paris##2
2. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person traveling to miami is the person playing bridge##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2     |      3       |
| Game   | monopoly | bridge      | chess  |
| Cigar      | alhambra   | vegafina   | tiparillo      |
| City        | edinburgh     | miami | paris |

