.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, prince
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, pilot, engineer
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, january, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the engineer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the chaman-smoker is between the pilot and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar    | prince     | chaman     | havana |
| Job       | engineer | lawyer | pilot |
| Birthday   | march     | september       | january    |

 